arStrings.szText: “How did Elias get a hold of the Sightless Eye?”
Not sure. As far as I knew, it was under the protection of the old rogue order—the Sisters of the Sightless Eye.
Heard some rumors that the years have not been kind to them.
They’ve suffered hardship before, but they’ve always clung on. Endured. As long as even one remains, so will the order and its traditions.
